{"tid":2075891,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳：初選缺物資 民主派籲捐iPhone - 李八方","createTime":"2020-06-23T06:42:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T06:24:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0c04b14990cf1e48c5a592f09a6aa8312e6e53c2","tid":2075891,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T06:42:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200623/3WEGQDHVHP4P257WLO4ORSE3VM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200623%2F3WEGQDHVHP4P257WLO4ORSE3VM%2F&d=%2FOWxXeQsMLcQIgbDBmmt7iNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=c2f4e88d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200623%2F3WEGQDHVHP4P257WLO4ORSE3VM%2F&h=5a3ffe99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200623/3WEGQDHVHP4P257WLO4ORSE3VM/</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：初選缺物資 民主派籲捐iPhone - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/APL3UTCMOC4DFWTPBKES2V6GCA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAPL3UTCMOC4DFWTPBKES2V6GCA.jpg&h=a7a2e2d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&lt;br /&gt;區諾軒（左）同戴耀廷積極準備下月初選。<br />\n<br />\n港大法律學系副教授戴耀廷同前立法會議員區諾軒等人計劃喺7月11同12日搞民主派初選，到時全港五區大約要開250個票站畀巿民投票，由於今次用電子投票，所以需要千幾部手機或平板電腦，不過佢哋已經要籌錢搞初選，冇額外錢再買手機或平板，所以佢哋呼籲巿民將舊iPhone或iPad捐出或借畀將協助搞初選票站嘅民主派議員辦事處，令初選順利進行。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n轉贈香港民意研究所<br />\n<br />\n區諾軒話目前初選面對最大技術困難，係未有足夠電子設備供票站用，因為唔想出現過去特首選舉公投期間，民主派電子投票系統畀黑客進行分散式阻斷服務（DDoS）攻擊而癱瘓，所以初選改為以「線下」投票模式做基礎，要票站人員透過手機或平板，再加初選團隊特設嘅程式，為投票巿民進行認證，...............................................<br />\n<br />\n戴耀廷亦喺fb話，今次係初選籌集得到嘅器材，將轉贈畀香港民意研究所。有意捐機市民可WhatsApp 6057 6197，安排交收事宜。"},{"pid":"0f504802c423754f94baafc6716df0b7eaa5b50e","tid":2075891,"uid":24641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T06:43:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實真係無得替代咩？"},{"pid":"b5a80717510791508b1d39e4fb16e921b708274b","tid":2075891,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T06:43:42.000Z","msg":"個topic 點解會變咗iphone <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明乜鬼舊tablet 都要"},{"pid":"544b41dbd97eb1073c7c511b3c269c0aa5ad9a41","tid":2075891,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T06:46:42.000Z","msg":"借"},{"pid":"3f3a14e93472cfdbf257718bbf0f9d50e34fb894","tid":2075891,"uid":145118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T15:00:44.000Z","msg":"去咗街站，佢哋話可以用自己手機，捐出嚟個啲係for長者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我已經對長者無乜期望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係黃，所以我同佢哋話會唔會太樂觀對於初選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ef7e21022e63214b8e9fa585d657b53b6c485e6","tid":2075891,"uid":145118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T15:07:32.000Z","msg":"仲話葵涌個到會由內排到外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我真係覺得太樂觀<br />\n我係FB&amp;連登都唔覺好多人撐初選<br />\n三投三不投仲要得6萬人簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過點都要踢走保皇黨<br />\n最後一次投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n35+成功率好微<br />\n但無理由自己人搞民意調查<br />\n整個初選都唔參與下<br />\n<br />\n啲人仲話初選係民主派搞<br />\n我問完搞手先知<br />\n根本唔係民主派搞初選<br />\n係自發性去搞<br />\n李伯盧呢個人提出三投三不投<br />\n戴耀廷就join咗幫佢<br />\n<br />\n民主派呢個濕鳩鍾意內鬥嘅派<br />\n點會自己搞呢啲初選嘢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講真咁多年民主派真係無乜作為<br />\n下下要靠市民自發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢點好討厭<br />\n不過好過民建聯啲仆街嘅"},{"pid":"9a7bfc7f381799b085f4c7d74e39213c5c4bfce5","tid":2075891,"uid":44358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T15:09:13.000Z","msg":"用開 ANDROID，冇ＩＯＳ產品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63ca9ac6b7fd700819a9e62f9d4010c78a4d6329","tid":2075891,"uid":145118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a7bfc7f381799b085f4c7d74e39213c5c4bfce5","tid":2075891,"uid":44358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T15:09:13.000Z","msg":"用開 ANDROID，冇ＩＯＳ產品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T06:24:28.000Z","msg":"話會出android"}]}